Gashora, ni umwe mu mirenge 15 igize Akarere ka Bugesera, ugizwe n’utugari dutanu ari two: Biryogo, Kabuye, Kagomasi, Mwendo, na Ramiro.

Umurenge wa Gashora ukora ku mugezi w’Akagera, no ku biyaga birimo icya Rumira, icya Gaharwa, na Kirimbi, na Mirayi.<ref>https://imvahonshya.co.rw/bugesera-ubuyobozi-bwasobanuye-gahunda-yo-kuhira-izafasha-mu-kurwanya-amapfa/</ref>




